title: Chermoula-Spiced Lamb Rump with Sumac Potato Wedges & Turnip Salad
description: A sumptuous lamb feast with a Middle Eastern twist. This tender lamb rump is spiced with chermoula, then paired
with crispy sumac wedges and a crunchy turnip salad. Don’t forget to rest your lamb for 10 minutes after cooking for
the perfect slices that are blushing and moist.

